  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/07512d881ccac770e1530f380bb7f13b.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/07512d881ccac770e1530f380bb7f13b.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/07512d881ccac770e1530f380bb7f13b.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a geometric world, you will have to fight the waves of cubes, spheres, and even pyramids, to defend your base! <br>                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/8bd93a6509e6d684f948b8f480a15741.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=300 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/8bd93a6509e6d684f948b8f480a15741.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/8bd93a6509e6d684f948b8f480a15741.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Light Towers</strong> is a Tower Defense game where you must build and strategically shoot your way through waves of enemies. Use various towers and weapons wisely to survive increasingly difficult levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/791c985a3bb82fdfc01f66f11c0f9cce.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/791c985a3bb82fdfc01f66f11c0f9cce.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/791c985a3bb82fdfc01f66f11c0f9cce.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>SHOOT!</strong><br><br>With your tower spaces being limited you need to use your weapons to reduce the enemy numbers. You will start with a basic weapon to help your towers in the defense and can buy 2 more different weapons to adapt to your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/01bd40a312503e40bda34424bb9001fa.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/01bd40a312503e40bda34424bb9001fa.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/01bd40a312503e40bda34424bb9001fa.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>BUILD!</strong><br><br>You have access to 4 different towers to defend your base, with different uses for each of them. At every level, you need to fill the different spaces with your choice of tower to support your strategy. Not all towers do the same, each will work for different occasions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/1aeac2e3e2ee9e34d8fa41b1f505f065.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/1aeac2e3e2ee9e34d8fa41b1f505f065.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/1aeac2e3e2ee9e34d8fa41b1f505f065.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>SURVIVE!</strong><br><br>Beat the odds as you progress through increasingly punishing levels, where a single mistake may cost you your victory. Use all your skills and your strategy to defend all the <strong>Light Towers!</strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/07512d881ccac770e1530f380bb7f13b.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/07512d881ccac770e1530f380bb7f13b.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/07512d881ccac770e1530f380bb7f13b.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a geometric world, you will have to fight the waves of cubes, spheres, and even pyramids, to defend your base! <br>                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/8bd93a6509e6d684f948b8f480a15741.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=300 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/8bd93a6509e6d684f948b8f480a15741.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/8bd93a6509e6d684f948b8f480a15741.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Light Towers</strong> is a Tower Defense game where you must build and strategically shoot your way through waves of enemies. Use various towers and weapons wisely to survive increasingly difficult levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/791c985a3bb82fdfc01f66f11c0f9cce.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/791c985a3bb82fdfc01f66f11c0f9cce.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/791c985a3bb82fdfc01f66f11c0f9cce.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>SHOOT!</strong><br><br>With your tower spaces being limited you need to use your weapons to reduce the enemy numbers. You will start with a basic weapon to help your towers in the defense and can buy 2 more different weapons to adapt to your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/01bd40a312503e40bda34424bb9001fa.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/01bd40a312503e40bda34424bb9001fa.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/01bd40a312503e40bda34424bb9001fa.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>BUILD!</strong><br><br>You have access to 4 different towers to defend your base, with different uses for each of them. At every level, you need to fill the different spaces with your choice of tower to support your strategy. Not all towers do the same, each will work for different occasions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/1aeac2e3e2ee9e34d8fa41b1f505f065.poster.avif?t=1727814898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/1aeac2e3e2ee9e34d8fa41b1f505f065.webm?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221850/extras/1aeac2e3e2ee9e34d8fa41b1f505f065.mp4?t=1727814898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>SURVIVE!</strong><br><br>Beat the odds as you progress through increasingly punishing levels, where a single mistake may cost you your victory. Use all your skills and your strategy to defend all the <strong>Light Towers!</strong></li></ul>",
